name: Affordable Cellular LLC
overview: Affordable Cellular management team has over 14 years of experience in the wireless industry. Affordablecellular.com was launched in 2010 to provide quality cellular phones, accessories and prepaid cellular services to its customers. What makes us different from our competitors? Quality, pricing and customer service. We are an accredited Better Business Bureau member. This partnership with BBB shows our commitment to sell top quality new, refurbished and used AT&T, T-Mobile and Verizon cell phones to customers seeking to replace their cell phones. Our unlocked GSM cell phones are refurbished by experienced technicians. New and used phones are also fully inspected and tested by our techs to meet our quality standards.
